Text: Can someone please, please, please upload the FULL original DVD version of this. Not an avi converted into a custom DVD! It costs more in postage than the cost of DVD itself to order it from the USA for delivery to Europe!!

This is not converted from an AVI, please read. As for me, I will not put up a DVDRip, maybe someone else will. I think this HQ MOV conversion is good and let's people know where to get better quality original DVD if they want. I know the crew says share, but I prefer to use versions like this for making free copies, personally. It seems right. Good luck.
